      <title>以可可闻名的科特迪瓦正面临不确定的未来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-14/cote-d-ivoire-known-for-its-cocoa-is-facing-a-democratic-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉萨内·瓦塔拉谋求第四个总统任期，这可能会破坏西非法语区最大经济体来之不易的政治稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-14/cote-d-ivoire-known-for-its-cocoa-is-facing-a-democratic-crisis</guid>
